title: #92Noon: Montage/Siny/Bercich/Czabe/Lavelle/PJ
description: Full show, starting with heavy focus on the Border Battle, with Sinykin on the hotline being smug and Bercich in studio. Steve Czaban joins midway through, Lavelle in studio most of final hour, and then PJ Fleck caps off the Monday party.
